        },
        {
          "name": "Journey",
          "color": "from-teal-500 to-emerald-500"
        }
      ],
      "shayaris": [
        {
          "id": 21,
          "text": "Life is but a fleeting moment,\nA story written with time's pen.\nCherish each chapter as it comes,\nFor you'll never read this page again.",
          "author": "Vikram Seth",
          "category": "Philosophical",
          "likes": 2100,
          "views": 7800,
          "shares": 410,
          "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1452421822248-d4c2b47f0c81?w=400&h=300&fit=crop",
          "mood": "philosophical",
          "tags": ["time", "moment", "fleeting"],
          "dateAdded": "2024-02-05"
        },
        {
          "id": 22,
          "text": "The river of life flows with twists and turns,\nTeaching us lessons at every bend we discern.\nSome chapters bring joy, others bring pain,\nBut each experience makes us wise again.",
          "author": "Neha Kapoor",
          "category": "Journey",
          "likes": 1870,
          "views": 6540,
          "shares": 290,
          "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1470114716159-e389f8712fda?w=400&h=300&fit=crop",
          "mood": "reflective",
          "tags": ["river", "lessons", "wisdom"],
          "dateAdded": "2024-02-10"
        },
        {
          "id": 23,
          "text": "Time is the currency we cannot earn,\nOnce spent, it will never return.\nInvest it wisely in things that last,\nFor the present moment quickly becomes past.",
          "author": "Rahul Mehta",
          "category": "Time",
          "likes": 2450,
          "views": 8900,
          "shares": 520,
          "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506784242126-2a0b0b89c56a?w=400&h=300&fit=crop",
          "mood": "thoughtful",
          "tags": ["time", "moment", "investment"],
          "dateAdded": "2024-02-15"
        },
        {
          "id": 24,
          "text": "Like a tree that weathers every storm,\nStanding tall through winters cold and warm.\nOur roots grow deeper with each test,\nMaking us stronger than all the rest.",
          "author": "Ananya Joshi",
          "category": "Struggles",
          "likes": 1780,
          "views": 6200,
          "shares": 310,
          "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1447752875215-b2761acb3c5d?w=400&h=300&fit=crop",
          "mood": "resilient",
          "tags": ["strength", "storm", "growth"],
          "dateAdded": "2024-02-18"
        },
        {
          "id": 25,
          "text": "The mirror of life shows our true face,\nReflecting choices we can't erase.\nEvery action, every deed,\nPlants a seed we'll one day need.",
          "author": "Karan Malhotra",
          "category": "Philosophical",
          "likes": 1980,
          "views": 7100,
          "shares": 380,
          "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505142468610-359e7d316be0?w=400&h=300&fit=crop",
          "mood": "introspective",
          "tags": ["choices", "consequences", "reflection"],
          "dateAdded": "2024-02-20"
        },
        {
          "id": 26,
          "text": "Life's not about the breaths we take,\nBut the moments that make our hearts awake.\nThe laughter shared, the tears we've known,\nThe love we've given, the seeds we've sown.",
          "author": "Priyanka Reddy",
          "category": "Lessons",
          "likes": 2300,
          "views": 8500,
          "shares": 490,
          "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500382017468-9049fed747ef?w=400&h=300&fit=crop",
          "mood": "inspiring",
          "tags": ["moments", "meaning", "purpose"],
          "dateAdded": "2024-02-22"
        },
        {
          "id": 27,
          "text": "The pages turn in life's great book,\nEach chapter brings a different look.\nSome lines bring joy, some bring tears,\nBut all will fade with passing years.",
          "author": "Arjun Patel",
          "category": "Journey",
          "likes": 1650,
          "views": 5900,
          "shares": 270,
          "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1454165804606-c3d57bc86b40?w=400&h=300&fit=crop",
          "mood": "poetic",
          "tags": ["story", "chapters", "time"],
          "dateAdded": "2024-02-25"
        },
        {
          "id": 28,
          "text": "Like waves that crash upon the shore,\nOur troubles come, then are no more.\nWhat seems so large will soon seem small,\nThis too shall pass - that's all.",
          "author": "Meera Nair",
          "category": "Philosophical",
          "likes": 2100,
          "views": 7700,
          "shares": 430,
          "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505228395891-9a51e7e86bf6?w=400&h=300&fit=crop",
          "mood": "comforting",
          "tags": ["troubles", "temporary", "waves"],
          "dateAdded": "2024-02-28"
        },
        {
          "id": 29,
          "text": "The clock ticks on without a sound,\nMarking time as it circles round.\nYesterday's gone, tomorrow's unknown,\nToday's the day that's yours to own.",
          "author": "Rishi Verma",
          "category": "Time",
          "likes": 1950,
          "views": 7000,
          "shares": 360,
          "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518632618333-09f6a5e9a8d1?w=400&h=300&fit=crop",
          "mood": "urgent",
          "tags": ["present", "moment", "opportunity"],
          "dateAdded": "2024-03-01"
        },
        {
          "id": 30,
          "text": "Life's garden grows with care and toil,\nSome flowers bloom while others spoil.\nBut every plant has its season to rise,\nUnder the same vast open skies.",
          "author": "Sunita Rao",
          "category": "Lessons",
          "likes": 1780,
          "views": 6400,
          "shares": 290,
          "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1466692476868-aef1dfb1e735?w=400&h=300&fit=crop",
          "mood": "hopeful",
          "tags": ["patience", "growth", "seasons"],
          "dateAdded": "2024-03-05"
        }
      ]
    },
    "motivational": {
      "name": "Motivational Shayari",
      "hindiName": "Motivational Shayari",
      "description": "Inspire yourself with powerful words that ignite passion and determination",
      "bgGradient": "from-orange-50 via-amber-50 to-yellow-50",
      "primaryColor": "orange",
      "secondaryColor": "yellow",
      "emojis": ["💪", "🔥", "🚀", "🏆", "🌟", "✨", "⚡", "👑", "🏅", "🌈"],
      "backgroundTexts": ["Success", "Victory", "Achievement", "Dreams", "Goals", "Ambition"],
      "subcategories": [
        {
          "name": "All",
          "color": "from-orange-500 to-yellow-500"
        },
        {
          "name": "Success",
          "color": "from-amber-500 to-orange-500"
        },
        {
          "name": "Dreams",
          "color": "from-yellow-500 to-red-500"
        },
        {
          "name": "Hard Work",
          "color": "from-red-500 to-orange-500"
        },
        {
          "name": "Perseverance",
          "color": "from-gray-500 to-orange-500"
        },
        {
          "name": "Self-Belief",
          "color": "from-purple-500 to-yellow-500"
        }
      ],
      "shayaris": [
        {
          "id": 31,
          "text": "The mountain seems high until you start to climb,\nEvery great journey begins one step at a time.\nDon't measure the distance, just take the first stride,\nFor impossible dreams with courage are tried.",
          "author": "Aditya Khanna",
          "category": "Success",
          "likes": 2650,
          "views": 9200,
          "shares": 580,
          "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464822759023-fed622ff2c3b?w=400&h=300&fit=crop",
          "mood": "inspiring",
          "tags": ["mountain", "journey", "courage"],
          "dateAdded": "2024-03-10"
        },
        {
          "id": 32,
          "text": "Stars can't shine without the dark,\nSuccess needs failure to make its mark.\nEvery setback is just a test,\nTo prove you want it more than the rest.",
          "author": "Nisha Sharma",
          "category": "Perseverance",
          "likes": 2300,
          "views": 8500,
          "shares": 490,
          "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534447677768-be436bb09401?w=400&h=300&fit=crop",
          "mood": "determined",
          "tags": ["failure", "success", "setback"],
          "dateAdded": "2024-03-12"
        },
        {
          "id": 33,
          "text": "Dreams are seeds that need your care,\nWater them with work and they'll grow there.\nThe soil of effort, the sunshine of will,\nWith patience and time, your garden will fill.",
          "author": "Rohit Malhotra",
          "category": "Dreams",
          "likes": 2450,
          "views": 8900,
          "shares": 530,
          "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519681393784-d120267933ba?w=400&h=300&fit=crop",
          "mood": "hopeful",
          "tags": ["dreams", "effort", "patience"],
          "dateAdded": "2024-03-15"
        },
        {
          "id": 34,
          "text": "The fire within burns bright and true,\nNo ocean of doubt can quench its hue.\nFeed the flames with faith so strong,\nAnd watch how you prove the doubters wrong.",
          "author": "Kavita Singh",
          "category": "Self-Belief",
          "likes": 2100,
          "views": 7800,
          "shares": 450,
          "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517976384346-3136801d605d?w=400&h=300&fit=crop",
          "mood": "passionate",
          "tags": ["determination", "faith", "doubt"],
          "dateAdded": "2024-03-18"
        },
        {
          "id": 35,
          "text": "Sweat today for smiles tomorrow,\nHard work saves you from future sorrow.\nThe pain of discipline or regret's sharp sting,\nChoose your struggle - it changes everything.",
          "author": "Vivek Oberoi",
          "category": "Hard Work",
          "likes": 2750,
          "views": 9500,
          "shares": 620,
          "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571019613454-1cb2f99b2d8b?w=400&h=300&fit=crop",
          "mood": "disciplined",
          "tags": ["discipline", "sacrifice", "future"],
          "dateAdded": "2024-03-20"
        },
        {
          "id": 36,
          "text": "The eagle learns to fly by falling,\nThe master first knew nothing at all.\nEvery expert was once a beginner,\nEvery winner first faced a sinner.",
          "author": "Anjali Mehta",
          "category": "Perseverance",
          "likes": 1980,
          "views": 7200,
          "shares": 410,
          "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509316785289-025f5b846b35?w=400&h=300&fit=crop",
          "mood": "encouraging",
          "tags": ["learning", "process", "beginner"],
          "dateAdded": "2024-03-22"
        },
        {
          "id": 37,
          "text": "Your limits exist only in your mind,\nBreak those chains and you will find.\nPotential unlimited, power so deep,\nAwaiting the courage to take the leap.",
          "author": "Rajiv Bajaj",
          "category": "Self-Belief",
          "likes": 2550,
          "views": 9100,
          "shares": 570,
          "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1461749280684-dccba630e2f6?w=400&h=300&fit=crop",
          "mood": "empowering",
          "tags": ["limits", "potential", "courage"],
          "dateAdded": "2024-03-25"
        },
        {
          "id": 38,
          "text": "The night is darkest before the dawn,\nYour struggle means success is being born.\nKeep moving forward through the pain,\nFor sunshine always follows rain.",
          "author": "Suman Grover",
          "category": "Perseverance",
          "likes": 2250,
          "views": 8300,
          "shares": 480,
          "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1530103862676-de8c9debad1d?w=400&h=300&fit=crop",
          "mood": "hopeful",
          "tags": ["darkness", "dawn", "struggle"],
          "dateAdded": "2024-03-28"
        },
        {
          "id": 39,
          "text": "Champions aren't made in gyms of gold,\nBut in arenas where stories of grit are told.\nWhere ordinary people do extraordinary things,\nBy the power of the spirit that within them sings.",
          "author": "Arun Joshi",
          "category": "Hard Work",
          "likes": 2400,
          "views": 8800,
          "shares": 520,
          "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571019614242-c5c5dee9f50b?w=400&h=300&fit=crop",
          "mood": "inspiring",
          "tags": ["champions", "grit", "spirit"],
          "dateAdded": "2024-04-01"
        },
        {
          "id": 40,
          "text": "Your current chapter isn't your whole story,\nThe coming pages will reveal your glory.\nKeep writing with courage, don't put down the pen,\nFor the best is yet to come - just wait till then.",
          "author": "Preeti Reddy",
          "category": "Dreams",
          "likes": 2150,
          "views": 7900,
          "shares": 460,
          "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1455390582262-044cdead277a?w=400&h=300&fit=crop",
          "mood": "optimistic",
          "tags": ["story", "future", "hope"],
          "dateAdded": "2024-04-05"
        },
        {
          "id": 41,
          "text": "The world will test your will each day,\nWith obstacles placed in your way.\nBut diamonds form under pressure's might,\nAnd gold is purified in fire's light.",
          "author": "Manish Kapoor",
          "category": "Perseverance",
          "likes": 2300,
          "views": 8400,
          "shares": 510,
          "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519125323398-675f0ddb6308?w=400&h=300&fit=crop",
          "mood": "resilient",
          "tags": ["pressure", "strength", "challenges"],
          "dateAdded": "2024-04-10"
        },
        {
          "id": 42,
          "text": "Success isn't about never falling down,\nBut rising each time you hit the ground.\nIt's the scratches that polish the stone,\nAnd the trials that make your strength known.",
          "author": "Deepika Malhotra",
          "category": "Success",
          "likes": 2500,
          "views": 9000,
          "shares": 550,
          "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500382017468-9049fed747ef?w=400&h=300&fit=crop",
          "mood": "determined",
          "tags": ["resilience", "failure", "rising"],
          "dateAdded": "2024-04-15"
        }
      ]
    }
